<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 1 lb meat</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (meat, not ground beef, ground beef chili is for dress-wearin' casters <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  get a good lean cut)<br>
